title: isBetween
description: checks if a value is between two other values (swaps min & max if min is greater than max)

rows.name: value
rows.description: value checked to see if it is between min and max

rows.name: min
rows.description: min value that value must be greater than (or equal too depending on config.endpoints)

rows.name: max
rows.description: max value that value must be less than (or equal too depending on config.endpoints)

rows.name: config
rows.description: config used to determine if the value is between min and max @see IsBetweenConfig
